{
  "stem": "21310.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The ghetto was surrounded by a 11-foot wall, a high wall, brick wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And on top of that you had barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were just a few gates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all of the Jews from Warsaw, and there were about 350,000-- one third of the population of Warsaw was Jewish before the war-- and people from all surrounding towns were put into the-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so at one point, in, I guess in 1941, there were almost half a million people squeezed in an area that was only 2% of the area of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we only could get one room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went on Sienna Street, which was the last street near the wall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And like-- and because part of the-- the ghetto was in a dilapidated section of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And only the-- the outer part was still in-- still had a few streets that were halfway decent, had halfway decent apartments.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents were lucky to get a room in a big apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was a three, four-bedroom apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, and it was one of those old-fashioned apartment with a dining room and-- and a big dining room, big-- big living room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got the dining room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember at that, oh, at that time, the-- the girl, Janina the maid, was not with us anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She went to-- to [NON-ENGLISH], back to her-- her family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After that point, she did not really want to leave us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in the ghetto-- she-- she wouldn't come into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the three of us stayed in this one dining room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember my mother strung some wire across the room.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
